---
const year = 2026;
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<footer class="main-footer">
    <div class="footer-container">
        <div class="footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-info">
        <a href={base} class="footer-logo-link">
            <img
                src={base + "/MPZ_logo_horiz_fullcolor_negative.svg"}
                alt="Marta Zola Logo"
                class="footer-logo-img"
            />
        </a>
        <p class="footer-tagline">Naturopatia integrata per il benessere femminile</p>
        <p class="footer-vat">P.IVA 14524810968</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-newsletter">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Newsletter</h4>
        <p>Iscriviti a "Semi": riflessioni e pratiche per radicarti nel corpo.</p>
        <form action="TUO_LINK_MAILERLITE" method="post" class="footer-form">
            <input type="email" name="fields[email]" placeholder="La tua email" required />
            <button type="submit" aria-label="Iscriviti">→</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-nav">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Menu</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href={base + "/chi-sono"}>Chi Sono</a></li>
            <li><a href={base + "/servizi"}>Servizi</a></li>
            <li><a href={base + "/contatti"}>Contatti</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-legal">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Social & Legal</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="footer-social">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/marta_zola_naturopata/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
                <span>Instagram</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p class="legal-disclaimer">Le pratiche proposte hanno finalità di accompagnamento e benessere e non sostituiscono diagnosi, terapie o il rapporto con il medico o altri professionisti della salute.<br/>
                In caso di necessità, rivolgiti sempre a un professionista sanitario qualificato.</p>
            <p>&copy; {year} Marta Zola. Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .main-footer {
        background-color: var(--accent-4);
        color: var(--bg-light);
        padding: 5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
        font-family: var(--font-body);
    }

    .footer-container {
        max-width: var(--container-width);
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1.2fr 0.8fr 1fr; /* Proporzioni bilanciate */
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .footer-logo-link {
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .footer-logo-img {
        height: 45px; /* Regola l'altezza desiderata */
        width: auto;
        display: block;
    }

    .footer-tagline {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-vat {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .footer-title {
        font-family: var(--font-headings);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
    }

    .footer-grid ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .footer-grid ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer-grid ul li a {
        color: var(--bg-light);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-grid ul li a:hover {
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .footer-newsletter p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .footer-form {
        display: flex;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* Linea sottile invece di un box pesante */
        padding-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .footer-form input {
        background: transparent;
        border: none;
        color: white;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        width: 100%;
        outline: none;
    }

    .footer-form input::placeholder {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }

    .footer-form button {
        background: transparent;
        border: none;
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 0 0.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-form button:hover {
        transform: translateX(5px);
    }

    .footer-social {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-social a {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--bg-light);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-social a:hover {
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .social-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .legal-disclaimer{
        font-size:12px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .footer-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
        }
        .footer-info {
            grid-column: span 2;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-nav,
        .footer-legal {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-social a {
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .footer-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-info {
            grid-column: span 1;
        }
        .footer-form {
            justify-content: center;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .footer-social a {
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }
</style>
